  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (NC-2 clean package)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. This package constitutes a fully compliant Minimal-profile UnitOfAssurance. All 13 credibility factors are assessed with achievedLevel meeting or exceeding requiredLevel. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification is performed across all five flow-speed operating points. Provenance is complete back to foundational experimental datasets. Decision: Accepted.",
